<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Karl von Eberstein zu Marktsteinach</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Niklas Wollsack, Bürger zu Nürnberg, den Nachlass des verstorbenen Engelhard Schmied bis Christi Himmelfahrt beisammenhalten wird, und verweist N. Pratbeck, Armmann des Adressaten, wegen seiner Ansprüche bis dahin auf den Rechtsweg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_5" id="1v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_5_r2l1">Karln von Eberſtein ʒu ſteynna geſeſſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_5_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Karl als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>Engelh<ex>art</ex></expan> ſmyds / vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> arm <expan>man<ex>n</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l3">Pratbeken <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu Rainfelt etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l4">ıſt vns wol fürbracht <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ etlıch <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> leẅt nach des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>engelh<ex>art</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l5">ſmyds <expan>ſelıg<ex>en</ex></expan> hab auch <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> vvıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Nıclas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l6">wollnſack bey dem der <expan>engelh<ex>art</ex></expan> ſmıd tod ıſt vnd der auch ſein hab noch Jnn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l7">hat beſant . vnd <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mıt Jm geredt / daʒ er <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>engelh<ex>art</ex></expan> hab / <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>rukt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l8">halten ſol . <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> dem auffarttag ſchıerıſt <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>end</expan> / Jn derʒeıt <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l9">wır <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>pratbeke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheınbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l10"><expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des Reıchs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l11"><expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / ob er des <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> . wenn dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe das antreff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l12">anheim ſein on geuerd / . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l13"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
