<ab>Karln von Eberstein zu Steynna gesessen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Karl, als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>Engelh<ex>art</ex></expan> Smyds und
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> arm<expan>man<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Pratbeken
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                        Rainfelt, etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und ist uns wol fürbracht
                                <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz etlich
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> lewt nach des
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Engelh<ex>art</ex></expan> Smyds <expan>selig<ex>en</ex></expan> hab
                        auch <expan>spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>; wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, Niclas Wollnsack, bey dem der
                                <expan>Engelh<ex>art</ex></expan> Smid tod ist und der auch sein hab
                        noch inn hat, besant und <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit im geredt, daz
                        er <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Engelh<ex>art</ex></expan> hab <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>rukt</expan>
                        halten sol <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> dem <app>
<note><q type="date">auffarttag schierist</q>25.05.1419</note>
</app>
<expan>kom<ex>m</ex>end</expan>. In derzeit <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>Pratbeke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, ob er des
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, wenn die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        die das antreff anheim sein, on geverd. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
